# m1_stuck_recovery.shot — fall hard, then try to escape with jet.
#
# Repeats m1_big_fall up to impact, then immediately fires jet to see
# whether the user-reported "I can sometimes escape via jet/jump" path
# works. Mostly looking for: does the body recover, or does it stay
# clipped through the floor while the jet thrust does nothing?

window 1280 720
seed   1 1
out    build/shots/recover
aim    520 920

at 10 shot stand_t010

# Climb.
at 30 press jet
at 130 release jet

# Fall.
burst falling from 140 to 240 every 20

# Impact frames.
burst impact from 245 to 295 every 5

# Try to escape via jet — fuel will partially refill on ground contact.
at 305 press jet
burst escape from 310 to 380 every 10
at 380 release jet

# Did we get back up? Did legs come unstuck?
burst settle from 385 to 500 every 20

at 540 end
